Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Yosemite
Description: Fun summer family trips full of camping and hiking. We completed a 7 mile hike!

Name: San Fransisco - Oakland Bay Bridge
Description: A very cool and windy place. I came here often to visit my sister.

Name: Big Bear City
Description: Winter visits full of building snowmen and having snowball fights with my family.

Name: Lake Havasu
Description: The first vacation I ever went on with my boyfriend. It was really hot there and I got so sunburnt.

Name: San Diego Zoo
Description: My first time being in San Diego was at the zoo, where there was so many cool animals and did lots of walking.
